column3: This is my first, hope I did it right.

The last two were very hard, especially the last one.  I sat here trying hard to figure something out but it just doesn't explain any reason really.  Being naive doesn't really make a reason why Colorado went to far with pot.  I did try!;#3 & #5 were hard, I truely did my best and am almost out of time, lol.  They didn't seem to have a clear reason though similar topic and wasn't sure what would be right to do there...;The last one just doesn't jive with why librarians are expendable.  Also, thanks for the reply to my comments :)  I had already left a good review but updated the communication rating to a 5 and left more feedback :) Thanks again!
